title: Google\Cloud\Dialogflow\V2\SessionEntityType
name: SessionEntityType
description:
Represents a session entity type.

Extends or replaces a developer entity type at the user session level (we refer to the entity types defined at the agent level as "developer entity types"). Note: session entity types apply to all queries, regardless of the language.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.dialogflow.v2.SessionEntityType
